:COMPILE_EXE
  ECHO Wait while preparing the build.
  ECHO ------------------------------------------------------------
  ECHO Cleaning Solution...
  %NET% %CLEAN_EXE%
  ECHO Compiling Solution...
  %NET% %OPTS_EXE%
